title: Boyle's Famous Corned Beef Co. Recalls Beef Products Due to Misbranding and Undeclared Allergen
summary: WASHINGTON, Nov. 25, 2015 Boyles Famous Corned Beef Co., a Kansas City, Mo. establishment, is recalling an undetermined amount of beef products due to misbranding and an undeclared allergen, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today.
